---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mangrove — Operational Consulting for Growing Businesses">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-label">Operational Consulting</span>
      <h1>Your business is complex.<br />It doesn't have to feel <span>out of control.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Mangrove helps growing businesses build the systems, processes and clarity they need — without the overhead of a full internal team. We come alongside you, implement real improvements, and stay for 12 months to make sure they stick.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a Free Consultation →</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn-secondary">See how we work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain Points -->
  <section class="pain-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Sound familiar?</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">You're making money. But it doesn't feel like it.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">
        Most advice focuses on one piece of your business. We look at how everything connects — because that's where real momentum comes from.
      </p>
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-card-icon">🔥</div>
          You're always firefighting. Every day is reactive. You're solving problems instead of building something.
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-card-icon">⛓️</div>
          The business runs on you. Take a holiday and things fall apart. That shouldn't be how it works.
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-card-icon">📊</div>
          You don't have the numbers you need. Something's not working — you just can't see where.
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-card-icon">🔁</div>
          Your team does things five different ways. Quality varies. Training new people takes forever.
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-card-icon">💸</div>
          Revenue is growing but profits aren't. You're working harder and seeing less return.
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <div class="pain-card-icon">📱</div>
          Your software is supposed to help. Instead it creates more work. You've adapted to it — it hasn't adapted to you.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who we help -->
  <section class="who-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Who we work with</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for businesses without a full internal function</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">
        You need strategic support — but not necessarily a full-time CFO or operations director. That's where we come in.
      </p>
      <div class="who-grid">
        <div class="who-card">
          <h3>Owner-operators</h3>
          <p>You've built something real. But you're carrying too much in your head. We help you get it out of your head and into systems that work without you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="who-card">
          <h3>Growing businesses</h3>
          <p>You've outgrown ad-hoc. But a full internal team doesn't make sense yet. We bridge that gap — delivering strategic capability without the overhead.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="who-card">
          <h3>Finance teams that are stretched</h3>
          <p>Your accounting function exists but it's reactive, manual, or running on spreadsheets that should have been retired years ago. We modernise and connect the pieces.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="who-card">
          <h3>Operations-led businesses</h3>
          <p>Service businesses, trades, professional firms — where delivery is everything and operational complexity is quietly killing your margins.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services teaser -->
  <section class="services-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">What we do</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Three ways we help</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">
        From a focused project to a 12-month partnership — we scale to what your business actually needs.
      </p>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-price">From $3,900/month</span>
          <h3>Ecosystem Audit</h3>
          <p>A focused review of your key business systems — where the friction is, what's costing you time and money, and the quickest wins to fix it.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-price">From $9,700/month</span>
          <h3>Ecosystem Transformation</h3>
          <p>Broader operational improvement across your whole business. We map, redesign and implement the systems and processes that actually run the place.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-price">From $900/month</span>
          <h3>Ongoing Advisory</h3>
          <p>Continuous access to strategic input, quarterly reviews and operational guidance — so you always have a thinking partner, not just a do-er.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to make your business work better?</h2>
      <p>Book a free, no-obligation consultation. We'll listen first.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book Your Free Consultation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
